timeline.bodyText:
@adriancole This logging created SO much noise in logs.
I suggest that it should be a lower level of logging (not INFO) or (and maybe in addition) let the logger be logger of LogFinishedSpanHandler and not the main Tracer.class logger so we can configure this logger specifically.
Currently the only way to reduce the noise is to change the Tracer logger to log only WARN and above.

